We then randomly decidehow many calls took place on this simulated day.
This is putting an large collection of numbered balls into a bag, with more balls with a given number on them if we historically had a large number ofdays with that number of calls received.
We then reach in and randomly pick out one of the balls, and use the number on it as the number of calls received in the day.
